description:
Marjorie Taylor Greene announces a proposed bill called the "Protect Children's Innocence Act," which would make it a felony to chemically castrate and perform "gender affirming" surgeries on children. Livid over flight cancellations and travel delays? Blame staff shortages. What’s the worst 3-letter government agency? The CDC is a cyclone of awfulness. Wrong about every single covid decision, relentlessly patronizing and politicized. It’s the most incompetent 3-letter agency in the federal government, which is saying a lot. C&B take your catcalls. Clay said today, "I'd like to be catcalled just once. Somebody out there, if you see me, please catcall me."
